verse.lines:
{lang-eng}A mind at perfect peace with God;
O what a word is this!
A sinner reconciled through blood;
This, this indeed is peace.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}By nature and by practice far,
How very far from God;
Yet now by grace brought nigh to Him,
Through faith in Jesus’ blood.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}So nigh, so very nigh to God,
I cannot nearer be;
For in the person of His Son
I am as near as He.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}So dear, so very dear to God,
More dear I cannot be;
The love wherewith He loves the Son,
Such is His love to me.{/lang-eng}
